description:
Worlds collide as the chaotic duo Jackal & Squidgirl Encounter Iverna Diskerna and her menagerie of freaks and dangerous monsters. All of them desire possession over the mysterious 'object' and many are willing to resort to extroardinary measures to possess it. Calamity will ensue.

Jackal's outrageous entrance to the auction sets the tone for the events to follow. Only one can posess the 'item' who will win the auction?

In the disastrous aftermath of the Auction, Jackal and the others must now contend with the threat of facing a King of Nightmare in his own domain.

The Temptation on the Mount (The Horrible Conflagration of Reality)

Stranded beyond the farthest reaches at the edge of the seas of reality Jackal must find his place within the universe and within himself lest he be destroyed by the darkness inherent in all things.

Who are you? What is your purpose? What is your truth?
